# Freshman Exemplifying Aggie Spirit Together

"Our mission is to develop freshmen into leaders who exemplify the Aggie Spirit and preserve the fundamental traditions and values of Texas A&M University through selfless service, community outreach, and University engagement. We envision creating a campus where all Aggies demonstrate the uncommon ability to inspire and lead the Aggie family to exceptional achievement."
